## Phase 1 Results Summary

- Phase 1.1: 6-gene epithelial reserve score AUC=0.558, below 0.65 target. NOT a severity proxy (no inflammation correlation).
- Phase 1.2: Epithelial score (0.558) underperforms TNF signaling (0.665) and integrin/trafficking (0.691). Target NOT MET.
- Phase 1.3: Expanded 13-gene panel (0.417) worse than original 6-gene (0.558). Best individual genes: SNX3 (0.705), CASP6 (0.699), GAS1 (0.676) — not classically epithelial.
- GSE73661 shows direction reversal (AUC=0.358) — needs analyst investigation.
- Overall: Phase 1 challenges the epithelial reserve hypothesis. Score captures independent biology but insufficient for treatment stratification alone.
